Package: dav.adrivencv
Type: Package
Title: Custom Templates and helper functions for building my CV with spreadsheets, based on datadriven-cv from Nick Strayer
Version: 0.2.2
URL: https://github.com/Davz33/dav_adrivencv, https://github.com/nstrayer/datadrivencv
Author: Davide Vitiello
Maintainer: Davide Vitiello <davide-vitiello@outlook.com>
Description: Separates the CV format from the content using spreadsheets, RMarkdown, and Pagedown. Built to allow easy out-of-the-box behavior, but also to allow you to go beyond the defaults with customization and lack of lock-in to a given format. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
